race.description: Ladbrokes Srm In Multis Dogs Final
race.comment: DESPICABLE PEDRO (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into second last time out (17.99) over 324m at this track. Likely to improve sharply this time. ISLE OF LACHLAN (3) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Recorded a nose win (17.75) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Can feature with the right run. DESPICABLE OTTO (5) won again in an impressive display after leading them home making it three straight at this track over 324m (17.67). The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Must be included in calculations.
